{"tid":1649270,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大量加入警隊可能係一個方法","createTime":"2019-10-12T14:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T17:25:36.000Z","uid":112167,"like":7,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"36e2a2aa36b62faba6b224ec68c9feeb0d4cce93","tid":1649270,"uid":112167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"今時今日黑警太多，政府又唔肯成立獨立調查委員會，黑警入邊嘅氣氛都係籠罩住打示威者嘅風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇影片都有講就算係支持成立獨立調查委員會嘅警察都唔夠膽出聲<br />\n會唔會反而係<strong>好大量</strong>啲人<em>唔係狗</em>加入警察，喺入邊改善返警察嘅風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會係一個解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能我發緊夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信今時今日狗只會越嚟越惡死，請原諒我可能係基督徒嘅心態，覺得改變人應該從佢哋嘅內心開始改變<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解有阻差辦公，但係冇阻示威者遊行<br />\n點解可以用警棍打人打到流血，但係唔可以比人自衛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps 如果有朝一日全部警察都係黃就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住發夢ing<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"839ee1d7c10b2a857ca8ac26a2787302713df0dd","tid":1649270,"uid":10520,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"on9仔"},{"pid":"acc7df1099351f5096280ec6825093dccc3b8d8f","tid":1649270,"uid":173598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"如果入面啲係武警呢？"},{"pid":"4792105dc42a8a0846407bb1e10de87906851447","tid":1649270,"uid":3409,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"你望下14年之後入去嘅黃c"},{"pid":"80a27f18be64902d438cc7116136d34003986dec","tid":1649270,"uid":159024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"三萬個黃都仲有幾千萬武警紅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5796559e9046d830e3479ef3616e8fab782a447f","tid":1649270,"uid":123053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"